## My process

### Built with

- Semantic HTML5 markup
- CSS custom properties
- Flexbox
- CSS Grid
- Mobile-first workflow


### What I learned

I learned javascript functionalities that how you can select an element and display the content of that element in another element. 

I also learned how to apply CSS styles using javaScript when an action is performed.

### Continued development

I want to improve my javaScript and make a better website.
I specially want to focus on javaScript logic building section and imagination of how the code is working.


